<L>__{exterior countryside day}
<A>__{the party travels through the emptiness.}
<L>__{exterior mountain pass dusk}
<A>__{his holiness walks beside his horse. he joins other members of the group standing on a ridge. tenzin gyatso picks up a rock and throws it over the side.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{"right will be victorious."}
<A>__{and now, the others do the same. the lord chamberlain says:}
<C>__{lord chamberlain}
<D>__{"the gods will be avenged!"}
<L>__{exterior outskirts of tibet day}
<A>__{the dalai lama sits before a low table set up on this desolate border. a document is before him.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{i repudiate the seventeen point agreement}
<A>__{with a slap of the state seal of tibet, this is done. the lord chamberlain removes this document and replaces it with another.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{i constitute the government of tibet, the only legal authority in the land.}
<A>__{the seal comes down hard once more. it is done.}
